text: Kalani Brooke Hilliker (born September 23, 2000) is an American dancer, fashion designer, model and actress. She became famous in 2013 on the Lifetime reality series Abby's Ultimate Dance Competition. Sne later appeared on Dance Moms. She was a regular cast member from 2014 to 2017.
